    {
      "name": "post_price",
      "docs": ["disc 17 (Engine B): the bounded pricer hot key refreshes the posted quote (price/band/conf + stamps) within the delta cap. data_slot and price_updated_ms in the body are IGNORED on-chain (re-stamped from the Clock sysvar) to defend phantom freshness; params_hash is folded to a u64 content stamp on-chain."],
