      "name": "set_status",
      "docs": ["disc 21: halt/un-halt a pool (BOTH PoolStateClmm and PoolStateAnchor; resolved by account disc). Guardian may HALT-only (set the type's halt bit); owner may set/clear any bit. bit > 7 => 6003. disable!=0 sets the bit (HALT); 0 clears (un-halt)."],
